name: My Happy Ending
author: Harmonix, Rhythm Authors
loading_phrase: This song is centered around a breakup and Avril bidding farewell to the possibility of a happy ending. After being dumped, she searches for answers and comes to the realization that her lover was insincere throughout the relationship. She puts most of the blame on his friends, for being a negative influence.

name: Stranglehold
author: Harmonix, Rhythm Authors
loading_phrase: Nugent didn't sing lead on this. Derek St. Holmes, who was the vocalist with his band, did. Nugent resented the attention Holmes received on stage and eventually sang all the hits himself. His explanation: "There's only one alpha wolf, and that's me".
